Hey Team! Today, as I was applying my mascara, a thought struck me ‚Äì does my beauty routine actually empower me, or am I just trying to meet society's expectations? In this episode, we're going to dive into the world of beauty standards and our own self-perceptions.

Let's explore how to feel confident from the inside out. Thanks for tuning in! Don't forget to subscribe and drop a comment with your thoughts, questions, or any topics you'd like me to cover next. Your input means the world! üí¨
